fields.name: Dr. Adesh Kumar Pandey
fields.message:
We are really proud of the student's club "Innogeeks", to develop knowledge of various technological domains including IoT, AR/VR, Web Development, Android Development & ML in its members and making them professionally prepared.
My warm wishes are with Team Innogeeks for their future endeavors!

fields.name: Ms. Nidhi Goyal
fields.message: Students today are more tech-savvy than ever before. A club like Innogeeks is very much needed to be present which gives students a platform to break the boundaries of imagination, think about innovative ideas & work upon them. Cheers to team Innogeeks for their work & best wishes for their future!

fields.name: Mr. Dinesh Kumar
fields.message: It gives us immense happiness and pride seeing the "INNOGEEKS" club of the Department of Information Technology achieving greater heights and success. My heartiest wishes to Team INNOGEEKS for their bright future!
